# Golrokh

> For using Golrokh API you need a TOKEN_KEY, if you don't have one,,please contact golrokh@sobhe.ir.

# Find Faces


## Request

> Request

```plaintext
{
    "datasets": [
        "siasi",
        "honari",
        "varzeshi"
    ],
    "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg"
}
```

```shell
curl  --request POST \ 
      --header "Content-Type: application/json" --header "Authorization: Token TOKEN_KEY" \
      --data-binary {
    "datasets": [
        "siasi",
        "honari",
        "varzeshi"
    ],
    "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg"
} \
      http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces
```

```python
from urllib2 import Request, urlopen

values = """
{
    "datasets": [
        "siasi",
        "honari",
        "varzeshi"
    ],
    "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg"
}
"""

headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json','Authorization': 'Token TOKEN_KEY',
}
request = Request('http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces', data=values, headers=headers)

response_body = urlopen(request).read()
print(response_body)
```

```java
import java.lang.System;
import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
import java.io.OutputStream;
import java.net.URL;
import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;
import java.net.URLConnection;
import java.io.InputStreamReader;
import java.io.BufferedReader;

class MyRequest {

    public static void main(String[] args){
        try{
            URL url = new URL("http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces");
            URLConnection con = url.openConnection();
            HttpURLConnection http = (HttpURLConnection)con;
            http.setRequestMethod("POST");
            http.setDoOutput(true);

            byte[] out = "{
    "datasets": [
        "siasi",
        "honari",
        "varzeshi"
    ],
    "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg"
}".getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);
            int length = out.length;

            http.setFixedLengthStreamingMode(length);
            http.setRequestProperty("Content-Type", "application/json");
            http.setRequestProperty("Authorization", "Token TOKEN_KEY");
            http.connect();
            try(OutputStream os = http.getOutputStream()) {
                os.write(out);
            }

            BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(http.getInputStream()));
            String inputLine;
            while ((inputLine = in.readLine()) != null)
                System.out.println(inputLine);
            in.close();
        }
        catch(Exception e){
            System.err.println(e);
        }
    }
}
```

```php
<?php

  $url = "http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces";
  $content = json_encode(
      '{
    "datasets": [
        "siasi",
        "honari",
        "varzeshi"
    ],
    "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg"
}');
  $curl = curl_init($url);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_HEADER, false);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, true);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER,
          array(
              "Content-Type: application/json",
              "Authorization: Token TOKEN_KEY",
              );
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_POST, true);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS, $content);

  $json_response = curl_exec($curl);

  $status = curl_getinfo($curl, CURLINFO_HTTP_CODE);

  if ( $status != 200 ) {
      die("Error: call to URL $url failed with status $status, response $json_response, curl_error " . curl_error($curl) . ", curl_errno " . curl_errno($curl));
  }


  curl_close($curl);

  $response = json_decode($json_response, true);
?>
```

```csharp
using System;
using System.IO;
using System.Net;
using System.Collections.Generic;

namespace MyRequest
{
    class Program
    {
        static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            var httpWebRequest = (HttpWebRequest)WebRequest.Create("http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces");
            httpWebRequest.Headers["Content-Type"]= "application/json";
            httpWebRequest.Headers["Authorization"]= "Token TOKEN_KEY";

            httpWebRequest.Method = "POST";

            using (var streamWriter = new StreamWriter(httpWebRequest.GetRequestStream()))
            {
                string json = "{
    "datasets": [
        "siasi",
        "honari",
        "varzeshi"
    ],
    "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg"
}";

                streamWriter.Write(json);
                streamWriter.Flush();
                streamWriter.Close();
            }

            var httpResponse = (HttpWebResponse)httpWebRequest.GetResponse();
            using (var streamReader = new StreamReader(httpResponse.GetResponseStream()))
            {
                var result = streamReader.ReadToEnd();
                Console.WriteLine(result);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

```json
  "image_url": "http://cdn.fararu.com/files/fa/news/1392/5/26/79742_241.jpg",
  "faces": [
    {

      "person_image": null,
      "probability": 0.91
    },
    {
      "box": "94 110 48 48",
      "person": "علی‌اکبر صالحی",
      "person_image": null,
      "probability": 0.72
    },
    {
      "box": "395 103 53 53",
      "person": "محمدجواد ظریف",
      "person_image": null,
      "probability": 0.7
    }
  ]
}

```

> For uploading image file you can send `multipart/form-data` request
> to this function:

curl -X POST --header "Authorization: Token TOKEN_KEY" -F "image=@FILENAME" -F "datasets=siasi,honari,varzeshi" http://HOSTNAME/api/find_faces

`POST /find_faces`

## Upload Image

> Request

```plaintext
"-----GOLROKH\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"image\"; filename=\"image.jpg\"\nContent-Type: image/jpeg\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: base64\n\\n\n-----GOLROKH\n"
```

```shell
curl  --request POST \ 
      --header "Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=---GOLROKH" --header "Authorization: Token TOKEN_KEY" \
      --data-binary "-----GOLROKH\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"image\"; filename=\"image.jpg\"\nContent-Type: image/jpeg\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: base64\n\\n\n-----GOLROKH\n" \
      http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces
```

```python
from urllib2 import Request, urlopen

values = """
"-----GOLROKH\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"image\"; filename=\"image.jpg\"\nContent-Type: image/jpeg\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: base64\n\\n\n-----GOLROKH\n"
"""

headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data; boundary=---GOLROKH','Authorization': 'Token TOKEN_KEY',
}
request = Request('http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces', data=values, headers=headers)

response_body = urlopen(request).read()
print(response_body)
```

```java
import java.lang.System;
import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
import java.io.OutputStream;
import java.net.URL;
import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;
import java.net.URLConnection;
import java.io.InputStreamReader;
import java.io.BufferedReader;

class MyRequest {

    public static void main(String[] args){
        try{
            URL url = new URL("http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/find_faces");
            URLConnection con = url.openConnection();
            HttpURLConnection http = (HttpURLConnection)con;
            http.setRequestMethod("POST");
            http.setDoOutput(true);

            byte[] out = ""-----GOLROKH\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"image\"; filename=\"image.jpg\"\nContent-Type: image/jpeg\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: base64\n\\n\n-----GOLROKH\n"".getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);
            int length = out.length;

            http.setFixedLengthStreamingMode(length);
            http.setRequestProperty("Content-Type", "multipart/form-data; boundary=---GOLROKH");
            http.setRequestProperty("Authorization", "Token TOKEN_KEY");
            http.connect();
            try(OutputStream os = http.getOutputStream()) {
                os.write(out);
            }

            BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(http.getInputStream()));
            String inputLine;
            while ((inputLine = in.readLine()) != null)
                System.out.println(inputLine);
            in.close();
        }
        catch(Exception e){
            System.err.println(e);
        }
    }
}
```

```php
  $curl = curl_init($url);

      die("Error: call to URL $url failed with status $status, response $json_response, curl_error " . curl_error($curl) . ", curl_errno " . curl_errno($curl));

?>
```

```plaintext
    "dataset": "siasi",
    "name": "فرد جدید",
    "image_url": ""
```
```shell
} \
```

```php
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_HEADER, false);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, true);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER,
          array(
              "Content-Type: application/json",
              "Authorization: Token TOKEN_KEY",
              );
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_POST, true);
  curl_setopt($curl, CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS, $content);

  $json_response = curl_exec($curl);

  $status = curl_getinfo($curl, CURLINFO_HTTP_CODE);

  if ( $status != 200 ) {
      die("Error: call to URL $url failed with status $status, response $json_response, curl_error " . curl_error($curl) . ", curl_errno " . curl_errno($curl));
  }


  curl_close($curl);

  $response = json_decode($json_response, true);
?>
```

```java
import java.lang.System;
import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
import java.io.OutputStream;
import java.net.URL;
import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;
import java.net.URLConnection;
import java.io.InputStreamReader;
import java.io.BufferedReader;

class MyRequest {

    public static void main(String[] args){
        try{
            URL url = new URL("http://api.sobhe.ir/golrokh/api/dataset_detail");
            URLConnection con = url.openConnection();
            HttpURLConnection http = (HttpURLConnection)con;
            http.setRequestMethod("POST");
            http.setDoOutput(true);

            byte[] out = "{
    "dataset": "siasi"
}".getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);
            int length = out.length;

            http.setFixedLengthStreamingMode(length);
            http.setRequestProperty("Content-Type", "application/json");
            http.setRequestProperty("Authorization", "Token TOKEN_KEY");
            http.connect();
            try(OutputStream os = http.getOutputStream()) {
                os.write(out);
            }

            BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(http.getInputStream()));
            String inputLine;
            while ((inputLine = in.readLine()) != null)
                System.out.println(inputLine);
            in.close();
        }
        catch(Exception e){
            System.err.println(e);
        }
    }
}
```
